---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services" description="Comprehensive grant and RFP support services for nonprofits, municipalities, and educational institutions.">
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-fog">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-deep mb-6">Our Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        We're more than writersâ€”we're partners in structure and stewardship.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Grant Strategy & Readiness</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Before you write, you need to know which opportunities are worth pursuing. We conduct prospect research, create alignment scorecards, and help you prioritize your grant calendar based on fit, capacity, and strategic goals.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Funder landscape analysis and prospect identification</li>
          <li>Alignment scoring and go/no-go decision frameworks</li>
          <li>Grant calendar development and prioritization</li>
          <li>Funding readiness assessments</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Prospect Research & Qualification</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Not all grants are created equal. We help you identify the best-fit opportunities and avoid wasting time on low-probability applications.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Comprehensive funder research and profiling</li>
          <li>Strategic fit analysis</li>
          <li>Competitive landscape assessment</li>
          <li>Timeline and capacity planning</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Narrative & Proposal Development</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          From concept to submission, we develop compelling proposals that connect your mission to funder priorities with clarity, evidence, and strategic structure.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Proposal architecture and narrative planning</li>
          <li>Full proposal writing and editing</li>
          <li>Executive summaries and cover letters</li>
          <li>Supporting documents and attachments</li>
          <li>Red-team review and quality assurance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Budgets, Attachments & Compliance</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Details matter. We ensure your budgets are accurate, your attachments are complete, and your submission meets every compliance requirement.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Budget development and review</li>
          <li>Budget narrative writing</li>
          <li>Attachment preparation and organization</li>
          <li>Compliance checklist and submission management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Reporting, Renewals & Stewardship</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Winning the grant is just the beginning. We help you build lasting relationships with funders through thoughtful reporting and strategic renewal planning.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Grant reporting and impact documentation</li>
          <li>Renewal proposal development</li>
          <li>Funder relationship management</li>
          <li>Stewardship strategy and communication</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-ridge-blue">Advisory Retainers</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          For organizations with ongoing grant needs, we offer monthly retainer relationships that provide consistent support, strategic guidance, and pipeline management.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Monthly grant calendar management</li>
          <li>Proposal drafting and review</li>
          <li>Regular strategy and pipeline meetings</li>
          <li>Progress tracking and outcomes dashboard</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-fog">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-8 text-center">Outcomes</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-8">
        Our clients win grants and RFPs because we focus on strategic alignment, rigorous structure, and evidence-backed narratives. While every organization's results vary, we measure success by win rates, funding secured, and the capacity we help build.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-12 text-center">Client Stories</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-fog p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-ridge-blue">Nonprofit</span>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">
            "Wellridge helped us secure $150,000 in foundation funding through strategic prospect research and compelling narrative development. Their alignment scoring saved us from pursuing three low-fit opportunities."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-fog p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-ridge-blue">Municipal</span>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">
            "We needed to respond to a complex state RFP with tight deadlines. Wellridge's systematic approach kept us organized and on track, resulting in a successful $500,000 award."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-fog p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-ridge-blue">Education</span>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">
            "As a small school district, we lacked internal grant capacity. Wellridge's retainer relationship gave us consistent support and helped us build internal knowledge over time."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-deep text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Request a portfolio review and let's discuss how we can help you win more grants.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-md text-lg font-medium hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
      >
        Request a Portfolio Review
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

